Question: Explain to a child how to do a task (e.g., cross the street).
Answer:
How to tie your shoes.  first you Take one shoelace in each hand, then you cross one hand over the other, after that take one shoelace and slide it under the triangle and pull tight.  Then make bunny ears with one of the shoelaces and take the other and wrap it around once.  Finally make another bunny ear with the other shoelace and slide in into the loop you just made.  Pull tight and youve tied your shoes.